Package: kbdcontrol
Architecture: kfreebsd-i386 kfreebsd-amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, debconf
Description: Command line tool to change keyboard layout
 Original FreeBSD command to set keyboard layout and the FreeBSD possible
 keyboards.

Package: net-tools
